LNG                          ← your Xcode project
├─ LNG                       ← app target (module)
│  ├─ LNGApp.swift           ← (already there) @main app entry
│  ├─ ContentView.swift      ← (already there) starter view; now loads DynamicPageView
│  ├─ Assets.xcassets        ← (already there)
│  ├─ Preview Content        ← (already there)
│  │  └─ Preview Assets.xcassets
│  ├─ DynamicUX              ← (NEW group)
│  │  ├─ Models              ← (NEW group)
│  │  │  └─ Models.swift     ← layout/page/section/component/action models + AnyCodable
│  │  ├─ State               ← (NEW group)
│  │  │  ├─ FormState.swift  ← flat key–value form store & bindings
│  │  │  └─ Conditions.swift ← tiny `when` expression evaluator
│  │  └─ Views               ← (NEW group)
│  │     └─ DynamicViews.swift  ← renderer (page/section/component + action button)
│  └─ spa_layout.json        ← (NEW) bundled sample layout JSON (add to app target)
│
├─ LNGTests                  ← (already there)
│  └─ …                      ← your default test stubs
├─ LNGUITests                ← (already there)
│  ├─ LNGUITestsLaunchTests.swift
│  └─ …
└─ Products (Derived by Xcode)




